[{"id":"VH908519","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<div><include href=\"../Passage/VH908517.qti.xml\" xmlns:xi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude\"></include></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">What should the students do before they cut the frame?</p>\n","rubricRef":"VH908519_rubric","features":[{"type":"sharedpassage","html":"<div class=\"stimulus_reference\" xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/apip/apipv1p0/qtiitem/imsqti_v2p2\" xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"><p class=\"introduction passage-intro\">Read this set of instructions.</p><div class=\"passage\"><div class=\"prose prose_type:instructions style:1\"><div class=\"title\"><p class=\"title_line passage-title\">かんたんファミリーツリーの作り方</p></div><p class=\"passage_para\">用意するもの</p><p class=\"passage_para\">家族やペットの写真</p><p class=\"passage_para\">大きい紙</p><p class=\"passage_para\">色えんぴつ</p><p class=\"passage_para\"><span class=\"glossary\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"glossary_term\">じょうぎ</span><span class=\"glossary_definition\">ruler</span></span></p><p class=\"passage_para\">テープ</p><p class=\"passage_para\">カッターナイフ</p><ol class=\"ordered_list style:2\"><li class=\"list_paragraph\">大きい紙に色えんぴつで木の絵をかく。その時、使う<span class=\"ruby\"><span class=\"rb\">写真</span> <span class=\"rt\">しゃしん</span></span>が何枚かをか考えながら木の<span class=\"glossary\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"glossary_term\"><span class=\"ruby\"><span class=\"rb\">枝</span> <span class=\"rt\">えだ</span></span></span><span class=\"glossary_definition\">branch</span></span>の本数を決める。</li><li class=\"list_paragraph\">使う写真の数に合わせて、木の枝のとなりにじょうぎを使って四角い<span class=\"ruby\"><span class=\"rb\">窓</span> <span class=\"rt\">まど</span></span>をかく。１本の枝に、２・３枚写真を付けると、バランスがいいですね。</li><li class=\"list_paragraph\">カッターナイフで窓を切りとり、フォトフレームにする。</li><li class=\"list_paragraph\">使う写真を窓より少し大きめに切る。</li><li class=\"list_paragraph\">紙の後ろから写真をテープではりつければ、ファミリーツリーのでき上がり。</li></ol><p class=\"passage_para\">＊ファミリーツリーは、自分の家族のことを、ほかの人に知ってもらいたい時に使うと便利ですよ！</p></div></div></div>"}],"choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Decide how many branches to draw</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Take several photos for the project</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Fold a large tree out of cardboard</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Use several colors to decorate</p>"],"answer":0}]